---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About T2H3 | True Trail Hash House Harriers">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-8 overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-red-700/40 bg-black shadow-2xl shadow-red-950/20 md:grid-cols-[1fr_320px] md:items-center">
      <div class="p-6 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-teal-300">
          About True Trail
        </p>

        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black text-white sm:text-5xl">
          True Trail Hash House Harriers
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-zinc-300">
          True Trail Hash House Harriers is a drinking club with a running
          problem. We follow flour, chase bad ideas, sing songs, and gather for
          trail, circle, and general hash foolishness.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-zinc-400">
          New hashers are welcome. You do not need to be fast, serious, graceful,
          or prepared. Bring a sense of humour, trail shoes, weather-appropriate
          gear, and enough cash for hash cash when required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-6">
        <img
          src="/images/logosmall.jpg"
          alt="True Trail Hash House Harriers logo"
          class="w-full max-w-[280px] rounded-2xl border-4 border-teal-400 bg-white p-3 shadow-2xl shadow-teal-950/40"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-red-500">
          Trail
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">Follow the marks</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-400">
          The hare lays trail. The pack follows. Sometimes the trail lies.
          Sometimes the pack lies harder.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-red-500">
          Circle
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">Songs and down-downs</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-400">
          After trail, the pack gathers for songs, accusations, announcements,
          and the occasional terrible decision.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-5">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-red-500">
          Pack
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-black text-white">All paces welcome</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-zinc-400">
          Runners, walkers, stumblers, shortcutters, and visitors are welcome.
          On-On!
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
